<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>공지 사항</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bbs.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
            integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
            crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/rootstyle.css" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>
{{>layout/navbar}}
{{>layout/sidebar}}
<div class="board_wrap">
    <div class="board_title">
        <h1>종합 종목 게시판</h1>
        <p>모든 종목의 사람들이 모여서 토론하는 중.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="board_list_wrap">
        <div class="board_list_wrap">
            <div class="board_list">
                <div class="top">
                    <div class="num">글 번호</div>
                    <div class="stock">주식종목</div>
                    <div class="title">제목</div>
                    <div class="writer">작성자</div>
                    <div class="date">작성일</div>
                    <div class="count">조회</div>
                </div>
                {{#posts}}
                    <div>
                        <div class="num">{{postOrder}}</div>
                        <div class="stock">{{stock}}</div>
                        <div class="title">
                            <a href="/posts/{{id}}">{{title}}</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="writer">{{writer}}</div>
                        <div class="date">{{formattedDate}}</div>
                        <div class="count">{{count}}</div>
                    </div>
                {{/posts}}
            </div>
            <div class="pagination">
                {{#hasPreviousPage}}
                    <a href="?page={{previousPage}}" class="btn">&laquo; 이전</a>
                {{/hasPreviousPage}}

                {{#pageNumbers}}
                    {{#isCurrent}}
                        <span class="current-page">{{number}}</span>
                    {{/isCurrent}}
                    {{^isCurrent}}
                        <a href="?page={{number}}" class="btn num">{{number}}</a>
                    {{/isCurrent}}
                {{/pageNumbers}}

                {{#hasNextPage}}
                    <a href="?page={{nextPage}}" class="btn">다음 &raquo;</a>
                {{/hasNextPage}}
            </div>
            <div class="bt_wrap">
                <a href="/posts/new" class="on">글쓰기</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{>layout/chatbot}}
</div>
</body>
{{>footer}}
</html>